{"type":null,"faqId":10602,"title":"P6-U06   如何启用屏幕解锁图案？","answer":"<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span> <span>&gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">安全</span> <span>&gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">屏幕锁定</span><span> &gt; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">图案。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在“选择您的图案”界面，通过手指在屏幕连续划过几个圆的圆心设定解锁时使用的图形样式，再点击“继续”。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">再次在屏幕上划过刚才的样式，点击“确认”完成解锁图形的设置。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;\">l<span style=\"line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:7pt;\"> </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">当点电源键或开关机时，手机会默认进入图案解锁界面，在该界面划过刚才的图案样式，进行解锁。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-indent:-12.2pt;margin-left:63.25pt;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=31782\" /><br />\n</span>\n</p>","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1329","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1397636640000,"seriesProductName":"EDGE-U00","visitedTimes":44,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justVie